title: CHULA VISTA FIRE SUPPORTS BREAST CANCER AWARENESS MONTH (City of Chula Vista, CA)
text: ( Source : City of Chula Vista, CA ) Across North America , firefighters are wearing pink during the month of October to support the fight against breast cancer. Chula Vista firefighters are participating by sporting pink shirts and hats.
